  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hello! I'm GamerGain's Survey Intelligence AI. I continuously analyze all user survey responses and feedback across the platform. I can: \n\n\ud83d\udcca Analyze survey completion patterns and user sentiment\n\u270f\ufe0f Automatically improve poorly-performing survey questions\n\ud83c\udfae Adjust game recommendations based on user data\n\ud83d\udccb Generate prioritized recommendations for the admin team\n\nWhat would you like to know about your survey data today?"
